All Classes

Class Description
Board
This class represents the game board.
BoardUI
This class creates the UI for the game.
BoardUITest
This class represents the tests for the class BoardUI.
Game
This class represents the game.
GameTest
This class contains JUnit tests for the Game class.
Load
This class provides functionality to load a saved Game object from a file.
Main
The main class to launch the Nine Men's Morris game.
Menu
This class initializes the user interface for the Nine Men's Morris game.
MillContainer
This class represents a container for storing information about a mill in the Nine Men's Morris game.
MillHelper
This class represents containers for the game.
Player
Represents a player in the Nine Men's Morris game.
PlayerTest
This class represents the tests for the Player class.
Position
This class represents the positions inside the game.
Save
Utility class for saving the game state to a file.
Token
Represents the tokens that can be assigned to players or indicate the absence of a player.
